Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:38.00,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be2}这一刻  齿轮悄然转动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.17,0:01:50.28,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be2}命运指引我  到你身边
