Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:21.51,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be2}再次矗立于这片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:24.66,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be2}此刻请君留步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:35.18,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,350)\be2}斩断心中软弱  正是你给予我的Justice of light
